summary: I had my eyes opened. I came to realize that I have more to offer this world than just making things that blow up. And that is...
caption:
I had my eyes opened. I came to realize that I have more to offer this world than just making things that blow up. And that is why, effective immediately, I’m shutting down the weapons manufacturing division of Stark International until such a time, as I can decide what the future of this company will be, what direction it should take, the one I’m comfortable with, and is consistent with the highest good of this country and the world.

Happy Birthday @kickassfu !!!

title: World's Apart
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2Q9bosh

by cookieonthescene

Best buds Steve and Bucky live a very regular and peaceful life. It’s consistent, predictable and stable.

Until it’s not.

One fine lazy morning they almost get killed by their dopplegängers, who claim they’re from a different universe and are Captain America and Winter Soldier.

They need to return to their own universe and they need to be fast, but is there really a way to go back? Can Steve and Bucky - two regular guys help them find the way out?

Biggest question of all - With things heating up between Captain America and Bucky while Steve catching feelings for the terrifying Winter Soldier, do they really want them to leave?

A multiverse fic where MCU! Captain America and Winter Soldier accidentally find get transported to a different universe which has no superheroes or superpowers.

They need to return to their own universe and they need to be fast, but is there really a way to go back? Can Steve and Bucky - two regular guys help them find the way out?

Biggest question of all - With things heating up between Captain America and Bucky while Steve catching feelings for the terrifying Winter Soldier, do they really want them to leave?

A multiverse fic where MCU! Captain America and Winter Soldier accidentally find get transported to a different universe which has no superheroes or superpowers.
